Description:
A Bygone Era

Inspection will not disappoint!

Description:
1/2 Acre (approx) ~ Ye Olde' Packing House
Room, room & room! Spread out families in this classic property set in the old Crib village.
Stylish 50's beach house (20 square) - fully renovated with 4 generous bedrooms, family sized kitchen - (d/w) with long island bench overlooking a sitting room and good sized
sunroom - gas ducted heating throughout.
Room to run on a large grassy yard and room to work or play in the fully restored packing house which once serviced adjacent orchards
- around 12 squares of open space - ideal studio/gym/offices etc.
Shady pergola, carport and rear lane access this is a gem!
